US President Donald Trump said on Saturday that he harbors no hostility towards China and hopes for better relations between the two countries. Trump made the marks in a meeting with Chinese President Xi Jinping on the sidelines of a summit of the Group of 20 major economies in the Japanese city of Osaka. 
